ad Malli</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Yusheng Han</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Melena Bellin</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Srinath Chinnakotla</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ty Dunn</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Timothy L Pruett</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Gregory J Beilman</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Jose Vega Peralta</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Mustafa A Arain</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Stuart K Amateau</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Sarah J Schwarzenberg</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Shawn Mallery</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Rajeev Attam</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Martin L Freeman</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2015Nov1 | American Journal of Gastroenterology, Vol. 110, No. 11</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/ajg.2015.297">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/s12262-015-1370-0"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s12262-015-1370-0">Diagnosis, Preoperative Evaluation, and Assessment of Resectability of Pancreatic and Periampullary Cancer</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ashish Verma</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Sunit Shukla</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Nimisha Verma</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">8 October 2015 | Indian Journal of Surgery, Vol. 77, No. 5</div><